The paper discusses a technique for blind recovery of signals or blind identification of mixtures in various applications, including antenna array processing, CDMA radio communication, and fluorescent spectroscopy. These applications involve signal processing, information theory, machine learning, and numerical analysis, which are all relevant to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: cs.IT (Information Theory), cs.SI (Signal Processing), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.SP (Numerical Analysis), and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper, ordered from most to least likely.
